    <item>
      <title>前托克集团首席运营官可能存在疏忽但并非犯罪，其律师称</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/ex-trafigura-coo-perhaps-negligent-but-not-criminal-says-lawyer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[托克集团前首席运营官迈克·温赖特的律师向瑞士法庭表示，温赖特可能存在疏忽，但他并不知道自己批准的付款是贿赂，据称是为了获得利润丰厚的安哥拉石油和航运合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/ex-trafigura-coo-perhaps-negligent-but-not-criminal-says-lawyer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 12:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
